# 05 — Landing Page

## Repositório

[github.com/gustavo-as/landing-page](https://github.com/gustavo-as/landing-page)

## Stack

- HTML + CSS puro
- Nginx (Alpine) para servir os arquivos estáticos
- Traefik para roteamento e SSL automático
- GitHub Actions para CI/CD

## Estrutura do projeto

```
landing-page/
├── .github/
│   └── workflows/
│       └── deploy.yml    ← pipeline de CI/CD
├── index.html            ← página principal
├── style.css             ← estilos
├── Dockerfile            ← build da imagem Nginx
├── docker-compose.yml    ← configuração do container + labels Traefik
└── .gitignore
```

---

## Dockerfile

```dockerfile
FROM nginx:alpine

COPY index.html /usr/share/nginx/html/index.html
COPY style.css /usr/share/nginx/html/style.css

EXPOSE 80
```

---

## docker-compose.yml

```yaml
services:
  landing-page:
    build: .
    container_name: landing-page
    restart: unless-stopped
    networks:
      - traefik-network
    labels:
      - "traefik.enable=true"
      - "traefik.http.routers.landing.rule=Host(`gustavohub.com`) || Host(`www.gustavohub.com`)"
      - "traefik.http.routers.landing.entrypoints=websecure"
      - "traefik.http.routers.landing.tls.certresolver=letsencrypt"
      - "traefik.http.services.landing.loadbalancer.server.port=80"

networks:
  traefik-network:
    external: true
```

---

## .github/workflows/deploy.yml

```yaml
name: Deploy to VPS

on:
  push:
    branches:
      - main

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
      - name: Checkout
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Deploy via SSH
        uses: appleboy/ssh-action@v1.0.3
        with:
          host: ${{ secrets.VPS_HOST }}
          username: ${{ secrets.VPS_USER }}
          key: ${{ secrets.VPS_SSH_KEY }}
          script: |
            cd ~/projects/landing-page
            git pull origin main
            docker compose up -d --build --force-recreate
```

---

## Primeiro deploy

### 1. Preparar a VPS

```bash
mkdir -p ~/projects/landing-page
cd ~/projects/landing-page
git clone https://github.com/gustavo-as/landing-page.git .
```

### 2. Configurar secrets no repositório GitHub

| Secret | Valor |
|---|---|
| `VPS_SSH_KEY` | Chave privada `~/.ssh/github_actions` |
| `VPS_HOST` | `187.124.32.146` |
| `VPS_USER` | `username` |

### 3. Fazer deploy

```bash
git add .
git commit -m "feat: initial landing page"
git push origin main
```

O GitHub Actions executa automaticamente e o site fica disponível em `https://gustavohub.com`.

